dc_description_s: This polygon shapefile shows area locations of pineapple plantations in Kenya, These data are originally from FAO's Africover dataset (2000).This data was used in Map 3.9 in Nature's Benefits in Kenya: An Atlas of Ecosystems and Human Well-Being.
